4051 Rouleurs 2016 TDF Recap

01 July 2017

Introduction

With the 2017 Tour De France set to commence wheels rolling tonight, its perhaps a good time to reflect on our performance twelve months earlier.

Yes - I came last.. by a long way.. and Im still sending this out.

With our 6 teams there was the opportunity for the selection of 54 unique riders in total. However the short list of favoured athletes in each category ultimately led us to select our squads from only 59 of the 198 riders starting the Tour at the Mont Saint-Michel island monastery on the 2nd of July, 2016.

Overall Team Performance

At the end of a tightly fought three week battle the Bandits skipped away with it. However it required bonus point allocations on the final stage for Dicks team to seal victory.
